that kind of question.

629
00:40:29,227 --> 00:40:30,595
Thank you very much.

630
00:40:47,612 --> 00:40:48,980
Hello, Ryota?

631
00:40:49,047 --> 00:40:50,882
What do you want for dinner?

632
00:40:52,384 --> 00:40:54,553
