752
00:49:21,659 --> 00:49:25,029
You are wrong to kick me out, Dad.

753
00:49:25,430 --> 00:49:26,731
Dad?

754
00:49:33,137 --> 00:49:35,773
You must remember me.

755
00:49:39,577 --> 00:49:42,280
Do you admit that
you are my father?

756
00:49:42,714 --> 00:49:43,815
Yes.

757
00:49:44,148 --> 00:49:47,585
But I truly think that
you should go home.

758
00:49:47,852 --> 00:49:49,954
Because you think I am troublesome.

759
00:49:50,054 --> 00:49:51,589
No.

760
00:49:51,856 --> 00:49:54,592
You will become dirty
if you stay in Tokyo.

761
00:49:54,859 --> 00:49:59,030
I can understand well
because I saw how you are doing.

762
00:49:59,230 --> 00:50:04,702
Now I also understand why
mom didn't say that you are alive.

763
00:50:04,902 --> 00:50:06,304
What do you mean?

764
00:50:07,271 --> 00:50:10,341
You met your daughter for
the first time in 15 years.

765
00:50:10,441 --> 00:50:12,744
And you tried to kick me back home.

766
00:50:15,046 --> 00:50:16,414
