790
00:52:54,472 --> 00:52:57,041
It's too late for Shinkansen
or express bus.

791
00:52:57,675 --> 00:52:59,210
Let me book a hotel.

792
00:53:00,444 --> 00:53:01,946
Let me hit you again.

793
00:53:02,547 --> 00:53:04,715
