798
00:53:13,758 --> 00:53:14,692
I know.

799
00:53:15,560 --> 00:53:17,929
Because your girlfriends visit here.

800
00:53:19,096 --> 00:53:20,631
I thought so.

801
00:53:20,898 --> 00:53:23,234
You and Hanako are in relationship.

802
00:53:25,770 --> 00:53:27,071
I am single.

803
00:53:27,338 --> 00:53:29,006
Ms. Okuno, a gym instructor,

804
00:53:29,173 --> 00:53:32,410
and Haruka at Chaconne also
come to see you, right?

805
00:53:32,743 --> 00:53:34,412
You must be busy.

806
00:53:34,679 --> 00:53:35,479
Hey!

807
00:53:36,047 --> 00:53:37,048
But Dad...

808
00:53:38,783 --> 00:53:39,817
You are deceived.

809
00:53:40,952 --> 00:53:41,986
